{"type": "article", "id": 26773, "title": "空气质量监测器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-13T06:34:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606081241590xhlnDkPgMqtKQXv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Dustin Jefferson Onghanseng 和朋友 Brian Lin 都患有呼吸系统方面的慢性疾病，在一次黑客松（<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hackathon\">hackathon</a>）活动上他们决定打造一款室内空气质量监测器，后来他们不仅赢得了那场黑客松，还以这个创意成立了一家初创公司。<a href=\"http://uhooair.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://uhooair.com/', 'uHoo');\" target=\"_blank\">uHoo</a> 正是这个同名公司的第一款产品，它可以持续监测房间内的空气质量（高级版还能监测温度和湿度等数据）并且通过专用的手机应用向你发出警报。你可以在应用上查看监测到的历史数据以及针对污染提供的一些建议。如果你对这个颇为智能的产品感兴趣的话，可以参与 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/uhoo-most-advanced-indoor-air-toxin-sensor#/\">Indiegogo</a> 上的众筹，基础版和高级版的最低早鸟价分别为 89 和 139 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124157sRc37glfrWPuhaE5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124157zCqm3VXDdgpFHoPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124158Qwlgt9Hzi7RnIyPj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608124158xf4euhcminMXRJdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}